gglFYYGZwgb_text","default":"<p>The kit is €69.99 instead of €90.</p><p>You save €20.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggNOYtAGI-h_text","label":"ggNOYtAGI-h_text","default":"<p>Yes.</p><p>But the kit saves you money — and gives you the full morning + night routine in one shot.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggSlD4p6ePO_text","label":"ggSlD4p6ePO_text","default":"<p>Yes.</p><p>Your order shows up in 24–48 hours.<br>Pay cash when it arrives.</p>"}],
